Title: Personal Reflection: Managing Timelines
Date: 2026-06-06
Source: mira_006_personal_reflection.pdf
Demo Persona: Mira Vale
Privacy Level: private

The gallery deadline is approaching quickly, and I felt overwhelmed this morning. To manage my stress, I broke the remaining tasks down into a day-by-day roadmap. Realizing that I have enough time if I stick to the schedule helped me regain my calm and start working productively.